7. Ng5
{ White has to react in the same fashion! There is no time for White to be stressed about Nf2 or Bf2! We just go forward with pressure on the f7 square! There are two move crucial ideas: f5! @@StartBracket@@to cancel out the connection between Bc8 and Ng4@@EndBracket@@ and in the case of any  7...Nf2  8.Qh5  with an even stronger attack on the f7 square! }
