9. O-O-O { White concludes the development and prepares for the butchering! }
9... h6 10. Bxh6 gxh6 11. Qxh6
{ Transposes into 8...h6?! 10.O-O O-O? 11.Bh6! gxh6 12.Qxh6 when White is clearly better with the idea of Bd3, followed by Nd5 or Ng5. Black can hardly defend the mate. }
