9... Qxf6
{ Even though it looks that Black solved the problem with a King, and he is only one step to the castle, this is a move that leads directly to losing position, and believe it or not Black failed for this in more than 168 games!! Black forgot the power of the Queen from d1! }
10. Nxe6 { After simple trade, Black's King will be vulnerable again. } 10...
fxe6 11. Qh5+
{ With a double attack on the King and the Bishop, White reaches a winning position with a piece up. This is a very common scenario in blitz games! }
