{ With the 6. e5! move, White enters the Max Lange attack opening! This is a very nice option for the club players as well as rapid and blitz players to complicate their games and win by following tactical lines. Max Lange offers interesting attacking positions, with many aggressive chances, and what makes it special - it is not that common in the practice! Would it be more surprising for you or for your opponent to end up there?! }
